#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:2334
#, no-wrap
msgid "# echo 'xc0     \"/usr/libexec/getty Pc\"         xterm   onifconsole  secure' >> /etc/ttys\n"
